The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Indias 300-plus scores on Day I abroad
India compiled 329 for four against Australia on the first day of the third Test in Melbourne on Friday. Following is the list of all 300-plus scores compiled by India on foreign soil.  372/7 vs South Africa, Bloemfontein, 2001-02  351/3 vs Sri Lanka, SSC, Colombo, 1998-99  334/1 vs Australia, Sydney, 1985-86  334/7 vs Pakistan, Faisalabad, 1982-83  329/4 vs Australia, Melbourne, 2003-04  329/7 vs Australia, Perth, 1977-78  324/4 vs England, The Oval, 1990  300/4 vs Sri Lanka, SSC, Colombo, 1993-94 Compiled by Ravi Kant Srivastava  Copyright 
